Handshake Dr. Catrenia just messaged you about an event Dr. Catrenia McLendon Academic Liaison/Project and Content Manager · 
IBM SkillsBuild Hi Ankita, I’d like to invite you to a live virtual event hosted by IBM SkillsBuild. What you’ll learn: * How to build a Retrieval-Augmented Generation (RAG) system using your own documents * Ho... View message IBM SkillsBuild Virtual Event Building Smarter RAG Systems with Muhammad Farooq Wed, Nov 19 ⋅ 5 pm–6 pm EST Virtual View message Mute You received this email because Handshake partners with your school to help you grow your career. Manage email preferences or unsubscribe . P.O. Box 40770, San Francisco, CA 94140
